    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278180/extras/75fbc05d2647b4b102cc9c21a826f28c.avif?t=1772033717\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278180/extras_big/75fbc05d2647b4b102cc9c21a826f28c.avif?t=1772033717 width=1560 height=684 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crystal Mountain Isle was once the biggest exporter of magic crystals; providing crystals to witches and wizards all over the world for generations - but then one day its exports suddenly stopped. The island has been shrouded in mystery ever since. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now stranded on the island, you explore, get to know its residents and uncover its secrets. Run around, swim, climb, fight dangerous foes and discover magical items to explore the island. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The whole island is a puzzle-box. As you explore, you'll find items that help you both reach new places and solve puzzles, revealing the great mystery of what happened here. Can you unravel the secret of Crystal Mountain?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
